---
// 关于我/简介组件
---

<section id="about" class="about">
	<div class="container">
		<h2 class="section-title">关于我</h2>
		<div class="about-content">
			<div class="about-text">
				<p class="about-description">
					我是一名普通的初级开发者，ACGN爱好者，音游玩家，喜欢研究技术，努力做喜欢的事情。
				</p>
				<p class="about-description">
					“顾盼两岸松山近，笑谈千古事如烟”
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.about {
		min-height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 6rem 2rem;
		background: #ffffff;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 800px;
		width: 100%;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #1a1a1a;
		text-align: center;
		margin: 0 0 4rem 0;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		position: relative;
	}

	.section-title::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		bottom: -1rem;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		width: 60px;
		height: 3px;
		background: #1a1a1a;
	}

	.about-content {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.about-description {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #4a4a4a;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		font-weight: 300;
	}

	.about-description:last-child {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.about {
			min-height: 100vh;
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.section-title {
			font-size: 2rem;
			margin-bottom: 3rem;
		}

		.about-description {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>

